                </annotation>
            </sentence>
            <sentence>
                <offset>359</offset>
                <text>He did not have any organomegaly.</text>
            </sentence>
            <sentence>
                <offset>393</offset>
                <text>His anthropometry showed weight of 10 kg (− 4 SD for age), height of 81 cm (−5 SD for age) and head circumference of 47 cm (−4 SD for age).</text>
            </sentence>
            <sentence>
                <offset>536</offset>
                <text>His hemogram and serum alkaline phosphatase were normal.</text>
            </sentence>
            <sentence>
                <offset>593</offset>
                <text>Radiographs revealed metaphyseal irregularities at knees.</text>
                <annotation id="10">
